Title: Power Ranger Samurai - The Complete Series

reviewText: This is a excellent collection of every episode from this season and series.  This new team of rangers learns  how to become samurai as well as save the world from Nighlok and their evil master.  The rangers also get a new ranger who taught himself to be a samurai and then came back to be a ranger and help the team defeat evil.
summary: Complete Series of Power Rangers Samurai
Title: Power Ranger Samurai - The Complete Series

reviewText: I ordered this last week. I am glad that this Season has been put out on DVD as a Complete Season. I got this item today and I am watching it right now. I have only one complaint and that is that the movie The Clash of The Red Rangers and both holiday specials are not in this set. I have them on DVD. I really am pleased with my purchase. I would recommend this to any fan of Power Rangers Samurai.
Title: Power Ranger Samurai - The Complete Series

reviewText: so here is a small photo slide show of what the box set looks like from the front, back and inside. this box set is not something i believe amazon should be blamed for. if you wanna blame anyone, blame lions gate for being lazy asses and not providing us with actual retail copies of these dvds rather than dvd-r's. i think my shadow puppet explains everything pretty well so watch and if i were you, please support this release:" get-puppet.com/s/wKhwfetkMhI?autoplay "FYI origins still has the opening theme with antonio in it. so that wasn't fixed since these dvds are in fact just copies of the official releases burnt onto dvd-r's. another side note, these are the same quality in terms of video and audio. i don't notice any loss of quality at all. check the puppet link above to hear what i have to say about this set. please support it as well.Power Ranger Samurai - The Complete Series
